    "headline": "American Tower Corporation Declares Quarterly Distribution",
    "summary": "BOSTON, May 21, 2026--American Tower Corporation (NYSE: AMT) announced that its Board of Directors has declared a quarterly cash distribution of $1.79 per share on shares of the Company’s common stock. The distribution is payable on July 13, 2026 to the stockholders of record at the close of business on June 12, 2026.",
